## 2. Profile Management (All Roles)

### Navbar Profile Modal
- **Every logged-in user** (customer, owner, staff, admin) sees a clickable profile button in the Navbar
- Clicking it opens a modal showing their **role**, **email/phone**, and an editable **name** field
- Saves via `PUT /api/auth/me`

### Owner Dashboard ‚Äî Profile & Performance Tab
Owners have a dedicated **Profile & Performance** tab in the restaurant dashboard with:

