## 3. Multi-Tenant Restaurant Isolation
- Each restaurant has its own owner, staff, and orders
- Owners can only see/manage **their own** restaurant's data
- Staff riders only see orders assigned to **their restaurant**
- Admin sees **all** restaurants globally

---

## 4. Delivery Staff Management

Owners can register internal delivery riders from the **Delivery Riders** tab:
- Enter rider name + phone number
- Rider can immediately log in from **`/login`** using phone-only login
- Riders appear in the assignment dropdown when dispatching orders

---

## 5. New Restaurant Registration Flow (Pending ‚Üí Active)
1. A new restaurant owner registers their account via `/register` (role: owner)
2. Their restaurant starts with `status: 'pending'`
3. Admin sees the pending restaurant in the dashboard (orange pulsing badge)
4. Admin clicks **"Accept"** ‚Üí restaurant becomes `active` ‚Üí customers can order

